markets.title: Will TOP 09 win the most seats in the 2025 Czech parliamentary elections?
markets.rules_primary: If TOP 09 wins more seats than any other party in the next Czech Chamber of Deputies election, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: If two parties are reported to hold the same number of seats following the election, then the party that had the highest vote share will resolve to Yes and all others will resolve to No. If the parties remain tied, the first party in alphabetical order will resolve to Yes and all others will resolve to No.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
